<statement>
<p>What is the solution to <m>\displaystyle{4}{x}+{7}={2}{x}+{11}</m>? <input type="text" style="width:4.6ch" name="qn0" id="qn0" value="" autocomplete="off" aria-label="Question 1" class="text"/> Â  </p>


