<solution>
<p><ul><li>2</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{4}{x}+{7}={2}{x}+{11}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{4}{x}+{7}-{11}={2}{x}+{11}-{11}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{4}{x}-{4}={2}{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{4}{x}-{4}-{4}{x}={2}{x}-{4}{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{4}=-{2}{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-\frac{{4}}{{-{{2}}}}=\frac{{-{2}{x}}}{{-{{2}}}}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{2}={x}</m>.</p>

</solution>
